text:
Hello <!here>,

Clearly lots of crazy confusion going on. Some people wanted to hangout this weekend so I created some spontaneous polls, but I forgot I was dealing with busy OMSCS Students. And that’s great- apologies for the confusion.

So clarification update:

November gathering will be:
When: November 12, 2022 at *1PM-3PM.* <-- I forgot again I might have violin lessons so changing to *Sunday November 13, 2022 (tell me if it’s a problem)*
Where: We will eat at a restaurant. TBD  <-- feel free to *nominate places* so I can make reservations if I can!

Activity before hand will be:
Top Golf in Alpharetta: 11AM-12/1PM.

If you’re interested in the smaller group going go-karting or eating Red and Green it’ll be on October 29, 2022. Give a shout in the thread above.

All right if you’re good to go please place in your final votes (and just choose one feel free to change your vote if you need to but no need to tap all three):
:+1: early thanksgiving meal and top golf
:golf:️ just top golf
:curry: just food
:rage: no I cannot come! <--but if interested just let me know what I can do to assist

Excited to see you all soon,
Cherie Lum
